node.text: Thank you ALL for the amazing birthday wishes today! The incredible thing is that I feel your love everyday, not just on my birthday. All your wonderful comments, questions and sharing of my book and podcasts makes me feel deeply grateful for each and every one of you! I can’t wait to travel the world and be able yo meet you all and give you a big hug for all the love you show me! It’s been a phenomenal year! From serving nurses and doctors on the frontlines, to sharing meditations with you all, releasing my first book, seeing @jayshettygenius go from strength to strength, launching @jayshettycertificationschool and seeing new leaders being created, announcing @samatea and interviewing some of my favorite people in the world on the podcast and working with them offline through to doing a fundraiser for dear India with my wife @radhidevlukia ~ Although there have been so many challenging moments I am so grateful to have the opportunity to serve. As monks we were always taught you can’t always find joy, or happiness in every moment but you can find service and when you find service you find everything you truly need. I promise you this is the only the beginning! There is so much more to come! I’m so deeply honored to have you in my life. Please remember you were made for a reason. If your journey has been tough it’s so that you can inspire others and help others with theirs. Today I am praying for each and every one of you. I am sending ALL my love and positive energy your way. I have so much more to say and I’ll be sharing it on my podcast this Friday! Lookout for a special birthday episode 🙌 with love and gratitude, always your well wisher, Jay
